<h1><%= @title %></h1>

<p>This is the site landing page.</p>
<p>As a starting point, we may want to list all (ones users brought over) Meetup groups here, by City. Maybe a group name search function to help quickly find a specific group.
</p>

<div class="groups">
  <h2>Meetup Groups</h2>
  <% @groups.each do | group | %>
  <div class="ea-group">
    <div class="group-img">
      <img src="<%= group.mu_thumb_link %>"/>
    </div>
    <div class="group-info">
      <ul>
      <li><a href="<%= group.mu_link %>"><%= group.mu_name %></a></li>
      <li><em><%= group.location %></em></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="group-desc">
    <%=raw group.description %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

